Leaf,is,a,platform,that,allows,merchants,and,their,customers,to,interact,Leaf,provides,merchants,with,tools,to,collect,payments,from,their,customers,and,ask,for,feedback,Leaf,provides,customers,with,an,application,to,retrieve,receipts,and,give,feedback,to,merchants,The,Leaf,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Leaf,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Public,documentation,is,not,available,interested,developers,should,sign,up,here,http,leaf,me,developers